  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Defend Legal Rights for Refugees in Greece</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The past year has brought seismic changes to the legal landscape in Greece. Refugees face a hardening of attitudes at domestic and EU level and an increasingly strict asylum process that emphasises speed and threatens the rule of law. In this context, comprehensive assistance from a qualified asylum lawyer can make all the difference. With your support, ELIL can continue to defend refugees&apos; rights by assisting them with their cases and helping reunite families across borders.</narrative>
  </description>
